e julep tin with mint leaves, then discard them before building the drink.\n  2. Follow standard julep building techniques.\n\nEach recipe lists a set of ingredients and a step-by-step guide on how to mix the drink, along with specific details for garnishing and serving. The document follows a typical cocktail recipe format with a clear, organized structure."
